body_html:
This looks like a great subproject that belongs in its own github repository. Since no one on the TensorFlow team would be able to maintain it, we can't accept PRs for this at the moment. If your issue is a question of how to implement this, the best venue for discussions of that sort is StackOverflow.

Thanks!
